    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 19–Tired and Thirsty.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第19课——又累又渴。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Why do the children thank their mother?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "孩子们为什么感谢他们的母亲？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "What's the matter, children?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "孩子们，怎么了？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "We're tired.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们累了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "And thirsty, Mom.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "还渴了，妈妈。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "Sit down here.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "坐在这里吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Are you all right now?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你们现在好些了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "No, we aren't.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "不，还没有。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "there's an ice cream man.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那里有个卖冰淇淋的人。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Two ice creams, please.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "请来两份冰淇淋。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Here you are, children.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "给你们，孩子们。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Thanks, Mom.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "谢谢，妈妈。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "These ice creams are nice.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这些冰淇淋真好吃。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Are you all right now?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你们现在好些了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "Yes, we are.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是的，好了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "谢谢。"
      }
    }
  ],
